 "You give him something that nobody else has. A heart. I have never seen him 
so focused and happy. Just trust me...he will make you happy. As a soilder 
and as a personal friend or mate. As for his past. He was trained by the best 
assains the council has. He then formed the group of our four horsmen. We 
have brought many pred victories togeather. But you are the first person he 
has ever taken orders from. He loves you."
